claim.claim-text:
An aroma capsule, comprising:
a heat-transfer container 120 defining a top opening 1200;
an aromatic substance 122 held in said heat-transfer container 120.

The aroma capsule as claimed in claim 1, further comprising a sealing film 124; and

said heat-transfer container 120 comprise a rim 1202 around the top opening 1200;

the sealing film 124 bonded to the rim 1202 of the heat-transfer container 120 to seal the aromatic substance 122 in the heat-transfer container 120, maintaining the quality of the aromatic substance 122.

The aroma capsule as claimed in claim 4, the breathing film 126 further comprise a border edge 1261;

the heat-transfer container 120 further comprise a rim 1202 around the top opening 1200;

said breathing film 126 bonded with the border edge 1261 thereof to the rim 1202 of the heat-transfer container 120 above the aromatic substance 122.
